title: IHEC, Iraq Elections 2010 : Former PM Allawi Leading, Iraq, March 22, 2010
name: IHEC, Iraq Elections 2010 : Former PM Allawi Leading, Iraq, March 22, 2010
description:
The poly shapefile shows a subset of 6 of Iraq's 18 provinces where former Prime Minister Allawi's party holds lead.

Look elsewhere for data on provinces where the current PM leading, Iran-backed party "National Unity" and Kurdish parties in the lead in northern provinces.

author.source: Iraq's Independent High Election Commission Website
